- Movie Ticket Booking System


==============================
6. BASIC CONCURRENCY (ONLY ESSENTIAL)
==============================

- synchronized / mutex
- thread-safe singleton
- producer-consumer (BlockingQueue idea)
- race condition basics


==============================
7. INTERVIEW ATTACK FLOW
==============================

Step 1: Identify entities (nouns → classes)
Step 2: Identify actions (verbs → methods)
Step 3: Identify variation point:
        - behavior changes → Strategy / State
        - object creation → Factory
        - add features → Decorator
        - notifications → Observer
Step 4: Start simple, then add pattern if needed


==============================
8. MOST IMPORTANT RULE
==============================

DO NOT force patterns.

Only use pattern when:
→ requirement changes OR interviewer asks flexibility
